Package com.ontotext.kim.model

Interface Summary
HashRegister.ContentProcessor This is a listener interface which provides means to perform bulk operations over all of the stored elements in the register.
 

Class Summary
AliasCacheImpl This class is designed to serve as an Alias dictionary for the KimGazetteer.
AliasCacheImpl.Stats The class is used to collect timing data for profiling purposes
AliasTextTransformer This class implements specific text normalization logic used by the class ParsingFrame.
ClassStatisticListener Gathers statistics on the classes of the entities loaded from the vocabulary.
DataFeedFactory  
EntitiesQueryListener  
EntityPriority  
HashedAlias This class represents an Entity Alias in the form of couple hash codes.

For this representation the text is considered a sequence of plain numeric and letter lexemes delimited by optional non-alpha-numeric character sequences of arbitrary length.
HashRegister This class implements a hash-code indexed storage for objects.
HashRegister.HashElement A container class that holds all of the stored objects with same hash-code value.
HashRegister.HashElementComp Comparator for sorting HashElement instances.
KIMDataFeed  
Options Options reader for the LKB Gazetteer
ParsingFrame This class is used as a text parsing tool by classes AliasCacheImpl and KimLookupParser and produces special output for the class HashedAlias.
The class provides means to parse a string into sequence of plain numeric and letter lexemes delimited by optional non-alpha-numeric character sequences of arbitrary length.
StatisticListener Gathers statistics on the entries in the entity cache.
